## Backend Structure

- [src/app/api](mdc:src/app/api) - API routes
  - [src/app/api/checkout](mdc:src/app/api/checkout) - Checkout API endpoints
  - [src/app/api/payments](mdc:src/app/api/payments) - Payment processing endpoints

